OL,3,CWoman and two boys critically ill
OL,4,Cafter being rescued from car
OL,6,FA woman and two boys are in a critical
OL,7,Fcondition in hospital following a
OL,8,Fserious incident near Bargoed, Rhymney
OL,9,FValley.
OL,11,FEmergency services, including two
OL,12,FWales Air Ambulance helicopters, were
OL,13,Fcalled to reports regarding the
OL,14,Fconcern for safety for three people in
OL,15,FGilfach on Sunday morning.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
