OL,3,CWoman and two boys critically ill
OL,4,Cafter being rescued from car
OL,6,FThe three people were seen in a car
OL,7,Fclose to Margaret Street shortly
OL,8,Fbefore 11am, a spokesman for Gwent
OL,9,FPolice said. Officers attended along
OL,10,Fwith personnel from the Welsh
OL,11,FAmbulance Service, Welsh Air Ambulance
OL,12,Fand South Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,13,FService.
OL,15,FA 36-year-old woman and two boys, aged
OL,16,Fnine and 16, were taken to hospital
OL,17,Ffor treatment.
OL,19,FAll three are in a critical condition,
OL,20,FGwent Police said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
