OL,3,CWoman and two boys critically ill
OL,4,Cafter being rescued from car
OL,6,FEnquiries into what happened are
OL,7,Fongoing.
OL,9,FA statement from the force read: "We
OL,10,Freceived a call regarding the concern
OL,11,Ffor safety for three people who were
OL,12,Fseen in a car close to Margaret
OL,13,FStreet, Gilfach, at around 10.45am on
OL,14,FSunday, April 19.
OL,16,F"Officers attended along with
OL,17,Fpersonnel from the Welsh Ambulance
OL,18,FService, Welsh Air Ambulance and South
OL,19,FWales Fire and Rescue Service.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
