OL,3,CWoman and two boys critically ill
OL,4,Cafter being rescued from car
OL,6,F"A 36-year-old woman and two boys,
OL,7,Faged nine and 16, were taken to
OL,8,Fhospital for treatment and all three
OL,9,Fremain in a critical condition.
OL,11,F"Enquiries are ongoing at this time."
OL,13,FA spokeswoman for the Wales Air
OL,14,FAmbulance service said: "I can confirm
OL,15,Fthe Wales Air Ambulance helicopters
OL,16,Fattended an incident in that region on
OL,17,FSunday.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
