OL,3,CWoman and two boys critically ill
OL,4,Cafter being rescued from car
OL,6,F"Our Dafen and Cardiff-based crews
OL,7,Fwere allocated at 11am and the first
OL,8,Fcrew arrived at the scene at 11.20am.
OL,9,FOur involvement concluded at 2.03pm."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/5
